        public Person​(int id,
              java.lang.String name,
              java.lang.String password,
              java.lang.String token,
              Person.PERMISSION permission)
        This constructor allow to create a user with an id, a name, a password, a token for a session to the services and boolean that is true if the user is an administrator, false if that is a customer.
        Parameters:
        id - the unique id for the user
        name - the name of a user, must be unique
        password - the password of a user
        token - the token for a session to use the services
        permission - Inform if the user is a customer or an administrator
